trans-unit.source: Contains a collection of instances of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> class.
Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> class.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> to add to the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
Adds a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> to the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
The position at which the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> was inserted.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> to locate in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
Determines whether the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> contains a specific <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" />.

<see langword="true" /> if the value of the <paramref name="header" /> parameter is found in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />; otherwise, <see langword="false" />.
The one-dimensional <see cref="T:System.Array" /> that is the destination of the elements copied from <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
The array must have zero-based indexing.
The zero-based index in the <c>array</c> parameter at which copying begins.

Copies the elements of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> to an <see cref="T:System.Array" />, starting at a particular index of the <see cref="T:System.Array" />.
The <paramref name="array" /> parameter is <see langword="null" />.
The <paramref name="index" /> parameter is less than zero.
The <paramref name="array" /> parameter is multidimensional.
-or-
The number of elements in the source SoapHeaderCollection is greater than the available space from the <paramref name="index" /> parameter to the end of the destination array.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> to locate in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
Determines the index of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
The index of the <paramref name="header" /> parameter, if found in the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />; otherwise, -1.
The zero-based index at which to insert the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> into the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> to insert into the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
Inserts a <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> into the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" /> at the specified index.
If the `index` parameter equals the number of items in the collection, then the <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader> is appended to the end of the collection.
trans-unit.target: 場合、`index`パラメーター、コレクション内の項目数に等しければ、<xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader>がコレクションの末尾に追加されます。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader> elements after the insertion point move down to accommodate the new element.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader>要素が新しい要素のため下にカーソルを移動後します。

The zero-based index of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> to get or set.
Gets or sets the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> at the specified index of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeaderCollection" />.
The <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" /> at the specified index.
trans-unit.target: 指定されたインデックス位置にある <see cref="T:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader" />。

trans-unit.source: This property provides the ability to access a specific element in the collection by using the following syntax: `myCollection[index]`.
trans-unit.target: このプロパティでは、`myCollection[index]` という構文を使用して、コレクション内の特定の要素にアクセスできます。

The <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader> elements that follow the removed <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader> move up to occupy the vacated spot.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader> 、削除された後にある要素<xref:System.Web.Services.Protocols.SoapHeader>繰りを上へ移動します。
